{"tid":2312992,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 12 再傳災情！蘋果證實無線充電恐失靈","createTime":"2020-12-05T12:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T06:24:46.000Z","uid":66351,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ab316afa09a215734422fd13e73336f7ada42d6d","tid":2312992,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:18:36.000Z","msg":"根據外媒《9to5mac》報導<br />\n蘋果於官方的客服支援證實<br />\n<span class=\"red\">iPhone 12 於無線充電確實有相關災情</span><br />\n預計在未來盡快修復。<br />\n<br />\n據悉綜觀國外各大論壇，有不少用戶反應 iPhone 12 系列放上無線充電版，一開始得以正常運作，後續卻可能忽然失靈<br />\n<span class=\"red\">《9to5mac》於實測中亦發生相同狀況</span><br />\n透過重新啟動 iPhone 得以恢復正常，但維持一兩天又會再有同樣的問題。<br />\n<br />\n網友向<span class=\"red\">官方支援求助，服務人員於線上證實</span>，蘋果正在著手處理相關問題，預計在未來幾天內獲得解決。<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">官方並沒有解釋出錯原因，以及目前的解決辦法。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sWLqNe3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsWLqNe3.png&h=5dd4cb55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a7e9f43a135711142252285e68bb4f032447655","tid":2312992,"uid":147376,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocOoy1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocOoy1A.gif&h=02e64a10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8302f344906434ba274bddc3d43c9de3f3f0aa56","tid":2312992,"uid":294,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LA2wHWr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLA2wHWr.gif&h=6d1b098f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18131dc665f4554e22f6ac3dd4140269da7b81b7","tid":2312992,"uid":158977,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T13:34:35.000Z","msg":"用家問題<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><p class=\"center\">此post已完</p></span>"},{"pid":"da968d3b1bda7997183b0c2cca116cb1e7530ced","tid":2312992,"uid":241072,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score"